WorldView-3 imagery acquired on grant from DigitalGlobe Foundation (http://www.maxmar.com).  

For imagery credit statements please follow the DigitalGlobe Foundation’s mandatory attribution guidelines:

Any use of the images in hardcopy print or broadcast must include the following credit reasonably displayed next to or
on the image: “Satellite image(s) courtesy of the DigitalGlobe Foundation”.  Any use of the images published on the
World Wide Web must include the following words, reasonably displayed: Copyright © 20XX DigitalGlobe Foundation or
Satellite image courtesy of the DigitalGlobe Foundation. Wherever possible, the word “DigitalGlobe Foundation” must be
hot-linked to the DigitalGlobe Foundation website (www.digitalglobefoundation.org). Each image must be individually
attributed.